sequenceDiagram
  participant User
  participant Chat as Chat adapter
  participant Executor as SkillExecutor
  participant DB as Quotes DB
  participant AC as AgentCash CLI
  participant API as Paid API

  User->>Chat: /research query
  Chat->>Executor: skill + canonical input
  Executor->>AC: check endpoint / estimate cost
  AC-->>Executor: quoted cost
  Executor->>DB: create quote(status=pending)
  alt below cap and no forced confirmation
    Executor->>DB: transition pending -> approved -> executing
    Executor->>AC: fetch with stored request
    AC->>API: paid call
    API-->>AC: result
    AC-->>Executor: result + cost
    Executor->>DB: transaction + quote succeeded
  else confirmation required
    Executor-->>Chat: quote confirmation button
    User->>Chat: confirm
    Chat->>DB: approve quote if status=pending
    Chat->>Executor: execute stored quote
    Executor->>DB: transition approved -> executing
    Executor->>AC: fetch with stored request
    AC->>API: paid call
    API-->>AC: result
    AC-->>Executor: result + cost
    Executor->>DB: transaction + quote succeeded
  end
  User->>Chat: replay same button
  Chat->>DB: transition fails
  Chat-->>User: replay rejected
